====Adjective====
{{en-adj|worse|worst}}

# Not [[good]]; [[unfavorable]]; [[negative]].
# Seemingly non-[[appropriate]], in [[manners]], etc.
#: ''It is '''bad''' manners to talk with your mouth full.''
